title: 5635 Flintridge Dr,Colorado Springs, CO 80918
description: Brazilian Cherry Wood Floors that flow throughout and the massive light wood vaulted ceiling over the Living Room, Dining Room, and Kitchen* The Great Room features a floor to ceiling brick gas log fireplace, walk-outs to the wrap around deck with incredible views, and has an open floor plan that is perfect for entertaining* The Gourmet Kitchen has granite countertops, double ovens, a center island with a gas cooktop, counter bar seating, and eat-in area with walk-out to the deck* The Formal Dining room is located just off of the Kitchen* There are 3 spacious Bedroom with adjoining baths and walk-in closets on the main level of this home*
